Ship: The Lark (hauler) [OWNED]: HP 4/23, AC 12 (+2 evasive), shield ready, burst ready. Weapons: Turrets ×2 (kinetic), Missile pod (missile, 3 left) (this is EXACTLY what it carries — invent nothing more).
THREAT BAND (enemy ceiling — the engine clamps fights to this): T3 — elite operators, warband cores. The player is well-armed enough for top-tier fights. A named BOSS may exceed the band as a set-piece; rank-and-file may not.
