Faction rep: Hollow Crown +3, The Undertow +2, Ledger network (Rook) +2, Meridian commerce +2, Rook Station street +0, Talos security -2, Sable Chain -2, The Wreckers -2, Free Drift +1, The Reclaimers +1, The Commons +0

